---
By: Nicholas of Cusa
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 300
    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Light
---
He who is worshiped as Light Inaccessible is not light that is material,
the opposite of which is darkness, but light absolutely simple and infinite
in which darkness is infinite light.
